text.tspan: Child mortality rate (IHME vs. UN estimates), 2015
Number of children per 1,000 live births who die before reaching the age of 5, as reported by the IHME Global Burden
of Disease database (GHBx) and the UN Child Mortality Estimates. When both sources have the same estimate the
values fall on the grey line.
